### 1. Login to get Token
# @name login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&username=admin&password=admin123

### 2. Add a New Skill
# Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with the token from the login response
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/skills
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Data Analysis",
    "description": "Learning Python and SQL for data"
}

### 3. Check Admin Dashboard
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE